SoulTraits: {
	Justice: {
		Name: JUSTICE
		Description: A soul that seeks fairness and truth.
		Bonus3: Gain a built-in triple jump.
		Bonus5: Increased critical strike chance by 6%.
		Bonus12: Increased projectile damage by 10%.
		Bonus20: Every 5 hits, gain a Justice Mark. \nYour next hit is guaranteed to critically strike.
	}

	Kindness: {
		Name: KINDNESS
		Description: A soul that nurtures and protects.
		Bonus3: +2 life regeneration to you. Heals nearby allies and town NPCs for 2 HP every second.
		Bonus5: When you or nearby allies take damage, increase your defense by +6 for 3 seconds.
		Bonus12: Potion effects are applied to nearby allies. +20% potion effect duration.
		Bonus20: When you or an ally dies, you and each ally gain a Kindness Mark. Increases total damage by 25% for 10 seconds.
	}

	Bravery: {
		Name: BRAVERY
		Description: A soul that charges forward without fear.
		Bonus3: +10% global damage to enemies within 10 tiles. Take 5% increased damage.
		Bonus5: +20% move speed while in combat.
		Bonus12: Taking damage increases damage dealt by 12% for 6 seconds.
		Bonus20: After dealing damage, gain a Bravery Mark. Increases global attack speed up to 20% based on enemy proximity.
	}

	Patience: {
		Name: PATIENCE
		Description: A soul that waits for the perfect moment.
		Bonus3: Enemies are less likely to target you.
		Bonus5: Gain double life regen speed while not moving.
		Bonus12: Gain access to Rogue Stealth. If you already have Rogue Stealth, increases maximum by 30.
		Bonus20: Every 30 seconds without taking damage, gain a Patience Mark. The next hit consumes the stack to reduce damage by 50%.
	}

	Integrity: {
		Name: INTEGRITY
		Description: A soul that stays true to one's self.
		Bonus3: +20% increased defense. -10% total damage dealt.
		Bonus5: Taking damage increases your damage dealt by 5%. Lasts 5 seconds, stacks up to 5 times.
		Bonus12: Removes all negative effects from previous investment bonuses.
		Bonus20: After taking damage, gain an Integrity Mark. Your next hit will add your Defense as flat bonus damage.
	}

	Perseverance: {
		Name: PERSEVERANCE
		Description: A soul that endures through hardship.
		Bonus3: Health pickups also restore mana. Mana pickups also restore health.
		Bonus5: +1% damage for each buff and debuff active on you.
		Bonus12: Gain up to +50 max health based on current mana, and +50 max mana based on current health.
		Bonus20: At full health, gain a Perseverance Mark. The next hit consumes the mark to deal 50% less damage, but depletes all mana.
	}

	Determination: {
		Name: DETERMINATION
		Description: A soul that refuses to give up.
		Bonus3: Reduced respawn time by 5 seconds.
		Bonus5: 6% increased global damage.
		Bonus12: Increased immunity frames when taking damage.
		Bonus20: At 50% health, gain a Determination Mark and store your position. On death, revive at half health and return to that position. 2 minute cooldown.
	}

	UI: {
		NoTrait: No Soul Trait
		VisitGerson: Visit Gerson to obtain a Soul Trait
